T1  - Stock splits: Signaling or liquidity? The case of ADR ‘solo-splits’
AU  - Muscarella, Chris J.
AU  - Vetsuypens, Michael R.
JO  - Journal of Financial Economics
VL  - 42
IS  - 1
SP  - 3
EP  - 26
